"M*ožete li mi pomoći?" (Can you help me?)
"P*ošaljite mi poruku kad stignete." (Send me a message when you arrive.)
"M*ožete da se odmorite u mom domu." (You can rest at my house.)
"G*ošće se moraju poštovati." (Guests must be respected.)
"M*ožete da izaberete bilo koji predmet." (You can choose any subject.)